@startuml
title TPL Conceptual Domain - Communication and UX

hide methods
hide stereotypes
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
left to right direction

class User
class Information
class InformationRead
class Favorite

Information "1" -- "0..*" InformationRead
User "1" <-- "0..*" InformationRead : read state
User "1" <-- "0..*" Information : authored by
User "1" <-- "0..*" Favorite : owner

note right of Favorite
Favorites can target different domain objects
(patient, episode, colloquium, coordination).
end note

@enduml
